error.message: Usage of deprecated trait Drupal\Core\Routing\UrlGeneratorTrait in class Drupal\form_mode_manager\Controller\EntityFormModeBase. Deprecated in drupal:8.0.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\Url instead.

Call to deprecated method redirect() of class Drupal\form_mode_manager\Controller\EntityFormModeBase. Deprecated in drupal:8.0.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use new RedirectResponse(Url::fromRoute()) instead.

Interface Drupal\form_mode_manager\EntityRoutingMapInterface extends deprecated interface Drupal\Component\Plugin\ConfigurablePluginInterface: Drupal\Component\Plugin\ConfigurablePluginInterface is deprecated in Drupal 8.7.0 and will be removed before Drupal 9.0.0. You should implement ConfigurableInterface and/or DependentPluginInterface directly as needed. If you implement ConfigurableInterface you may choose to implement ConfigurablePluginInterface in Drupal 8 as well for maximum compatibility, however this must be removed prior to Drupal 9.
Call to deprecated method url() of class Drupal\Core\Config\Entity\ConfigEntityBase. Deprecated in drupal:8.0.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Please use toUrl() instead.

Usage of deprecated trait Drupal\Tests\taxonomy\Functional\TaxonomyTestTrait in class Drupal\Tests\form_mode_manager\Functional\FormModeManagerUiTest. Deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Tests\taxonomy\Traits\TaxonomyTestTrait instead.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to form_mode_manager.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
